Class Failure<SuccessType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.geode.services.result.impl.Failure<SuccessType>
  • Type Parameters:
    SuccessType - the result type for a successful operation. Not used by the Failure type but required by the ServiceResult
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Result<SuccessType,​java.lang.String>, ServiceResult<SuccessType>
    public class Failure<SuccessType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServiceResult<SuccessType>
    This type of ServiceResult represents a failed operation. It contains the errorMessage for the failure.
